data.description: Wonderfully maintained three bedroom home in Hopewell School District situated on a corner lot!  The main floor of the home includes the living room, dining room, kitchen and half bath. The living room features a beautiful bay window and opens to the dining room, off of the dining room you'll find a large, private deck perfect for relaxing and entertaining. The updated kitchen includes all appliances and offers a pantry for extra storage. Three bedrooms and an updated bath can be found upstairs and there is ample extra storage in the basement which walks out to the large, fully fenced, backyard!
